authors: Francois Botha, Jan Havlíček, Aleksei Pankratev, Manuel de Leon, Amir Ghezelbash
description: See release notes https://github.com/ClosedXML/ClosedXML/releases/tag/0.100.3 . ClosedXML is a .NET library for reading, manipulating and writing Excel 2007+ (.xlsx, .xlsm) files. Formulas are not evaluated. It aims to provide an intuitive and user-friendly interface to dealing with the underlying OpenXML API.
